# VibeStream Discovery & Mobile Excellence

We have completed the "Discovery & Parity" roadmap, culminating in a high-fidelity mobile experience and intelligent content detection.

## Phase 21: Mobile Playback Excellence
Refined the platform for premium interaction on all devices.
- **Touch-Tuned Controls**: Increased the horizontal spacing and horizontal tap-areas for the Like, Hype, and Share buttons on mobile viewports.
- **Mobile Halo Optimization**: Throttled the Halo Engine (ambient glow) sampling rate on small screens to prioritize playback smoothness while maintaining visual flair.
- **Touch Progress Bar**: Implemented `onTouchMove` support for the video progress bar, allowing for precise scrubbing on mobile.
- **PWA Polish**: Deployed high-fidelity 192x192 and 512x512 manifest icons with a gold-on-black luxury aesthetic.
- **Shorts Logic Sync**: Updated the `is_short` auto-classification to include aspect-ratio detection, ensuring vertical uploads are automatically routed to the Shorts player.

## Phase 22: Engagement & Distribution Polish
Implemented highly robust engagement tracking and premium social sharing UI.
- **Strict View Tracking**: Upgraded the `increment_view_count` logic. Views now require a minimum of **5 seconds of active, uninterrupted playback** to register, fighting bots and spam.
- **Premium Share Sheet**: Replaced raw clipboard copy with a custom Framer Motion Share Modal, including integrations for X (Twitter), Facebook, WhatsApp, and Email.
- **Smart Description UI**: Transformed the video description into an expandable component. It intelligently extracts the [Category](file:///C:/GOLive/components/CategoryBar.tsx#24-51) and [Tags](file:///C:/GOLive/app/upload/page.tsx#299-308) from the raw metadata and renders them as high-visibility, branded badges.
- **Subscription Audit**: Audited the `subscriptions` schema and confirmed the exact presence of `subscriber_id`, ensuring the backend matches the frontend [SubscribeButton](file:///C:/GOLive/components/SubscribeButton.tsx#16-133) constraints.

